  "Has no time": [
   {
    "text": "A word in the participle of Hebrew or Aramaic does not alone tell us what time the action happened. This is like the English word \"running,\" which only describes an action, not when it happened. We require the context of the sentence to determine the time of the action.",
    "type": "text"
   }
  ],
  "In the past": [
   {
    "text": "The participle can be used in the past tense, for example הוא היה כותב, ",
    "type": "text"
   },
   {
    "type": "italics",
    "tokens": [
     {
      "text": "hu haya koisev",
      "type": "text"
     }
    ]
   },
   {
    "text": " meaning \"he used to write\" or \"he used to be writing.\" If you wanted to say \"he wrote,\" ie a one-time past event instead of an ongoing past event, you would just use the regular ",
    "type": "text"
   },
   {
    "text": "past tense",
    "type": "global",
    "tokens": [
     {
      "text": "past tense",
      "type": "text"
     }
    ],
    "targetSubtopic": "Past tense",
    "targetTopic": "Past tense",
    "enclosingTopic": "Participle constructions",
    "enclosingSubtopic": "In the past"
   },
   {
    "text": ", and not the \"past-tense version\" of the participle.",
    "type": "text"
   }
  ],
  "In the present": [
   {
    "text": "The participle can be used in the present tense by adding a noun before the verb, for example, הוא כותב, ",
    "type": "text"
   },
   {
    "type": "italics",
    "tokens": [
     {
      "text": "hu koisev",
      "type": "text"
     }
    ]
   },
   {
    "text": ", meaning \"he is writing\" or \"he writes.\"",
    "type": "text"
   }
  ],
  "In the future": [
   {
    "text": "The participle can be used in the future tense, for example, הוא יהיה כותב, ",
    "type": "text"
   },
   {
    "type": "italics",
    "tokens": [
     {
      "text": "hu yiyeh koisev",
      "type": "text"
     }
    ]
   },
   {
    "text": ", meaning \"he will be writing.\" If you wanted to say \"he will write,\" ie a one-time future event, you would just use the regular ",
    "type": "text"
   },
   {
    "text": "future tense",
    "type": "global",
    "tokens": [
     {
      "text": "future tense",
      "type": "text"
     }
    ],
    "targetSubtopic": "Future Tense",
    "targetTopic": "Future Tense",
    "enclosingTopic": "Participle constructions",
    "enclosingSubtopic": "In the future"
   },
   {
    "text": " and not the \"future version\" of the participle.",
    "type": "text"
   }
  ],
